            <h2 class="c-card__title">Assessment + Roadmap</h2>
            <div class="c-card__body">
              <p>Do you have some disconnected pieces of a design system, but you want to take it to the next level? I can help your teams get unstuck by conducting an thorough discovery process with key representatives from design, dev, product, and stakeholders. Then I'll put together an assessment based on that feedback, including a roadmap with practical recommendations for next steps.</p>
              <p><a href="/contact/" class="c-button">Send Request</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="c-card">
            <h2 class="c-card__title">Oversight and Support</h2>
            <div class="c-card__body">
              <p>Design systems work is so tightly coupled with organizational change, I've found that ongoing partnerships end up being the most successful. We'll go through a discovery process together, and but I'll make myself available for an agreed upon time to you or folks from your team to answer any questions and provide ongoing DS guidance needed — on a call, in an email, or on Slack.</p>
              <p><a href="/contact/" class="c-button">Contact Me</a></p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="l-grid__item">
          <div class="c-card">
