            <div class="c-card__body">
              <p>Do you have a competent design systems team in place, but need some expert advice? Are you a startup founder wanting some guidance on which toolstack makes the most sense for your needs? Need some ideas how to get more folks at your organization to use the design system you've already built? Book a 1-on-1 call and ask me anything about the DS challenges you're facing. There will be limited prep for these calls, but I'll give you or your team practical advice that they can put into action right away.</p>
              <p><a href="/contact/" class="c-button">Book A Call</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="c-card">
            <h2 class="c-card__title">Design System Workshop</h2>
            <div class="c-card__body">
